text: Her onginð embe þises middaneardes yldo.
Seo forme yld is fram Adame oð noe, þæt is þonneIXhund wintra &LXXVIwintra.
Ðonne is seo oþer yld fram noe oð abraham þæt is þonneCCCwintra &XCVIIwintra.
Ðonne is seo þridda yld fram abrahame oð moisen þæt is þonneIXhund geara &LXXgeara.
Ðonne is seo feorðe yld fram moysen oð dauid, þæt is þonneCCCCgeara, &XCIIIIgeara þæs forðgewitenes þære miclan burge babilonie.
Ðonne is seo fifte yld fram dauid oð Cristes tokyme þæt is þonne fif hund geara &LXXXIXgeara.
Ðonne is seo sixte yld fram Cristes akennednysse oð þissere worulde ende.
Ðonne fram middaneardes fruman oð Christes akennednysse, þæt is þonne six þusend geara &Cgeara &XXVgeara &IXmonðas.
Ðonne fram þissere worulde oð Christes þrowungtid, þæt is þonne six þusend geara, &Cgeara &LVIIIgeara.
